(2104, 160944, '2012-09-27 15:15:20', '"In the CA3 region only the second subtype was\ndetected with similar morphological characteristics.\nIn addition to stratum radiatum some of them innervated\nstratum oriens as well (Fig. 4)."', 'p 303 right top', 'data', NULL, NULL),
