(2228, 161030, '2012-09-27 15:15:22', '"In str. pyr. [pyramidale] of the CA1 area, boutons colabelled for VGLUT3 [vesicular glutamate transporter type 3] and GAD [glutamic acid decarboxylase] were also positive for CCK [cholecystokinin] (Fig. 5A).  These triple labelled boutons were in close contact with the soma and proximal dendrites of principal cells and interneurons."', 'p 557 right bot', 'data', NULL, NULL),
