(2231, 161032, '2012-09-27 15:15:22', '"We tested CR [calretinin] and CCK[cholecystokinin]-immunolabelling in VGLUT3[vesicular glutamate transporter type 3]-positive somata in the CA1 area.  Somatic CCK- or CR- labelling occurred alone in 32.7% and 54.8% of the cells, respectively.  There was no colocalization between CR and VGLUT3, or CR and CCK (Fig. 7B and Table 2).  Likewise, none of the tested VGLUT3-positive cells in the CA3 area/dentate gyrus (123 cells) and isocortex (40 cells) was immunoreactive for CR."', 'p 559 left bot', 'data', NULL, NULL),
