(2319, 161054, '2012-09-27 15:15:23', '"Figure 1. Characteristic morphologies and immunocytochemical profiles of NGFCs [neurogliaform cells] in the dentate....  DJ: Recorded and confirmed NGFCs in the den-\ntate filled with biocytin (x100) express a variety of NGFC markers, including COUP TFII [chicken ovalbumin upstream promoter transcription factor 2(D,E), nNOS [neuronal nitric oxide synthase (F,G), and reelin (G), and NPY [neuropeptide Y] (HJ). Each\nimage represents a single fluorescent channel, with biocytin indicating the recorded cell (D,F,I) and the adjacent panels indicating individual antibody labeling in the same plane of focus (E,G,H,J). The brightness and contrast of these images were digitally adjusted to provide maximal visualization of the markers."', 'p 1481, Fig. 1', 'data', NULL, NULL),
